  "texts": [
    "2025) highlighted the impact of edge ordering schemes.",
    "These analyses remain limited: they cover few tasks, single sources of variation, or only discuss aggregate results (Chu et al. 2025).",
    "In contrast, we propose a systematic decomposition of serialization schemes and assess sensitivity across a broad set of reasoning tasks.",
    "We study, in particular, the role of fine-tuning and evaluate its impact in generalizing to unseen tasks.",
    "LLMs on Graphs and Graph SerializationsProcessing graphs with LLMs."
